title: Feds Californians in flood areas should buy insurance now
text:
Feds: Californians in flood areas should buy insurance now 
CBS 46 Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Heavy rains that brought a flood threat to North and Central Texas will spread into South Texas on Sunday as a stalled cold front causing the downpours is reinforced by remnants of Hurricane Patricia....
